<p>If available, go to <strong>Setup » Client » [Select client] » Categories » Settings</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Select the maximum number of levels in the category navigation.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> (<span class="icon green"><i class="psicon-save"></i></span>) the settings.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
</div>
</div>
